  "description": "OBSCURA coupling. Drama parked precisely at the Kuramoto critical boundary (0.45). Without OBSCURA, the field hovers at the edge of phase transition. With OBSCURA's mass-spring input, each oscillation pushes the field PAST the threshold and snaps it back — a repeating earthquake of synchrony. The voice locks and breaks, locks and breaks, in time with OBSCURA's physics.",
